body: "GH-603. After a lossy merge resolution (.toon taken from one side, history union-merged), pm history-repair re-anchors by appending a reverting patch that discards the other author's mutation from effective state; validate then reports drift 0 / ok:true. A teammate agent's change is reverted invisibly — data loss is cemented. Fix direction: repair must emit an explicit revert warning naming discarded events/authors, expose a post-repair divergence signal in validate/health, and document a re-application recovery path. Detection half = pm-ol3p strict verify gate."
